This paper presents a new mathematical method for stochastic optimal control problems and applies it to the task of autonomous driving. The paper involves concepts from control theory, machine learning, and information theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
